                <p class="text-base md:text-xl font-normal text-justify">
                    We've built subsidiaries across Asia, Europe, and the
                    Americas – and we can help you do the same. Our partnership
                    of IT enthusiasts, founders, former Big Corp managers,
                    technologists, and sales & market strategists spans both
                    sides of the Atlantic, bringing deep expertise in US and
                    European IT markets and a commitment to providing both
                    strategic guidance and hands-on support.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="px-4">
