                            CONNECT ON LINKEDIN
                        </a>
                    </dd>
                    <dd class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 text-s ">
                        <span
                            id="short-description-2"
                            class="short-description line-clamp-3"
                          >
                          With over 30 years in High Tech, Merlin Yamssi is a visionary leader who empowers businesses to embrace the future
                        through digital transformation... 
                        </span>
                        <span
                            id="full-description-2"
                            class="hidden full-description"
                        >
                        With over 30 years in High Tech, Merlin Yamssi is a visionary leader who empowers businesses to embrace the future
                        through digital transformation. With 30+ years of experience across industries, he
                        leverages cutting-edge technologies like AI, Cloud, and Web3 to unlock new
