                        clients, crafting pragmatic strategies, and turning ideas into impactful solutions. He is
                        a trusted advisor, a strategic thinker, and a catalyst for growth in the digital age.
                        </span>
                        <a
                            id="toggle-link-2"
                            href="#"
                            class="text-[#B6CB23] hover:text-gray-500 italic underline mt-2 toggle-link"
                        >
                            Read More
                        </a>
                    </dd>
                </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Team Member 3 -->
                <div class="mx-4">
                    <div
                        class="relative rounded-3xl p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-900/10 bg-[#F6F6F6] shadow-2xl"
                     >                    
                    <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900 flex flex-col items-center md:flex-row md:items-start">
                           
                        <div class="mb-2 items-center justify-center">
                            <img class="" src="images/robert.png" alt="" />
                        </div>
                        <dd class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Robert Gessner </dd>
                    </dt>
                    <dd
                        class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 text-sm font-medium"
                    >
                        Partner
                    </dd>
                    <dd
                        class="text-base leading-7  text-gray-600 text-s flex items-center"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="images/svg/linkedin.svg"
                            alt="LinkedIn"
                            class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 object-contain"
                        />
                        <a
                            target="_blank"
                            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/robertgessner/"
                            class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 italic underline"
                        >
                            CONNECT ON LINKEDIN
                        </a>
                    </dd>
                    <dd class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 text-s ">
                        <span
                            id="short-description-3"
                            class="short-description line-clamp-3"
                          >
                        With over 25 years of international IT industry experience, Robert has held leadership roles
                        in sales, operations, and market strategy across EMEA and global markets...
                        </span>
                        <span
                            id="full-description-3"
                            class="hidden full-description"
                        >
                        With over 25 years of international IT industry experience, Robert has held leadership roles
in sales, operations, and market strategy across EMEA and global markets. He led
international sales planning, sales operations, and strategic Go-to-market programs. He
scaled operations and sales processes across EMEA and APAC. Robert is known for driving
